    저희는 세상이 아직 깨닫지 못한 옳은 일, 해야하는 일을 하고, 그 가치를 전달합니다. </h2>
</div>

<div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <div style="margin-top: 80px;">
        <p class="h1">Members</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 150px; margin-top: 100px;">
            <div class="col-lg d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="width: 250px;">
                <div class="mr-5"><%= image_tag('W_img_recruit_jisoo.png', class:"recruit-img")%></div>
                <div>
                    <p class="h6">CEO. Founder</p>
                    <p class="h4">강 지 수</p>
                    <p class="h6">편견없는 기획자</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="width: 250px;">
                <div class="mr-5"><%= image_tag('W_img_recruit_ahram.png', class:"recruit-img")%></div>
                <div>
                    <p class="h6">CDO. Co-Founder</p>
                    <p class="h4">김 아 람</p>
                    <p class="h6">아직 젊은 디자이너</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    

    <div class="mt-5 mb-5">
        <p class="h1 text-center">Recruit</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-5">
        <p class="h2 text-center">“사용성 테스트에 대한 이해와 관심을 가지고 있고,</p>
        <p class="h2 text-center">자유로운 분위기 속에서 함께 즐기며 일할 수 있는 엔지니어를 찾습니다”</p>
    </div>
    

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center" style="margin-top: 80px;">
        <div class="recruit-explain" style="margin-right: 180px;margin-top: 20px;">
            <p>모집분야&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;엔지니어</p>
            <p>모집인원&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0명</p>
            <p>자격요건 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1. 플랫폼 개발 경력 2~3년 이상</p>
            <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2. 빅데이터 분석 처리 경험 有</p>
            <p>지원기간&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;채용 시까지</p>
            <p>지원서류&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;이력서, 자기소개서, 포트폴리오</p>
        </div>
        <div style="width: 480px;">
            <%= form_with(model: @post, local: true, url: "/recruitsubmit") do |form| %>
            <% if @post.errors.any? %>
            <div id="error_explanation">
            <h2><%= pluralize(@post.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this post from being saved:</h2>

            <ul>
            <% @post.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
            <li><%= message %></li>
            <% end %>
            </ul>
            </div>
            <% end %>
            <div class="recruit-input-box"><label>이름*&nbsp;&nbsp;</label><input class="recruit-input" type="text" id="uname" name="name"></div>
            <div class="recruit-input-box"><label>연락처*&nbsp;&nbsp;</label><input class="recruit-input" type="text" id="phone" name="phonenumber"></div>
            <div class="recruit-input-box"><label>이메일*&nbsp;&nbsp;</label><input class="recruit-input" id="emailAddress" type="email" name="email"></div>
            <div class="d-flex recruit-input-box">
            <div style="margin-top: 10px;width: 30%"><label for="file ">파일 업로드*</label></div>
            <div class="d-flex flex-column " style="width: 60%;">
            <div class="recruit-inputfile-box">
        
            <%= form.file_field :attachment %>
            </div>
            <div class="recruit-inputfile-box">
                
            <%= form.file_field :attachment2 %>
            </div>
            <div class="recruit-inputfile-box">
            
            <%= form.file_field :attachment3 %>
            </div>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <button class="recruit-button">더 테스터 지원하기</button>
            </div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    $(".navbar-nav a:nth-child(4)").addClass("color");

    var inputs = document.querySelectorAll( '.inputfile' );
    Array.prototype.forEach.call( inputs, function( input )
    {
        var label	 = input.nextElementSibling,
            labelVal = label.innerHTML;

        input.addEventListener( 'change', function( e )
        {
            var fileName = '';
            // if( this.files && this.files.length = 1 ){
            //     fileName = e.target.value.split( '\\' ).pop();
            // }
            if( fileName ) {
                label.querySelector( 'span' ).innerHTML = fileName;
            }
            else {
                label.innerHTML = labelVal;
            }
        });
    });
</script>